ghmm
------------------------------------------
General Hidden Markov Model Library

Runtime requirements:
  bash-5.2.21-1
  cygwin-3.6.10-1
  libghmm-devel-0.9rc3-1bl1
  libghmm1-0.9rc3-1bl1
  libxml2-2.10.4-2
  pkg-config-2.5.1-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  autoconf-15-3
  automake-20250528-1
  binutils-2.46.1-1
  cygport-0.37.7-1
  gcc-core-14.4.0-1
  libtool-2.5.4-1
  make-4.4.1-2

Canonical website:
  https://sourceforge.net/projects/ghmm/

Canonical download:
  mirror://sourceforge/ghmm/ghmm-0.9-rc3.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack ghmm-0.9rc3-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./ghmm-0.9rc3-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/ghmm-0.9rc3-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/ghmm-0.9rc3-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libghmm1-0.9rc3-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libghmm-devel-0.9rc3-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

